      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver version controlled and documented; unit tests pass for all hemolysis sub-models.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R1 used under institutional license with version control. All relevant solver modules verified against published benchmark cases. SQA documentation complete and archived."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
