      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Normalized index of agreement for hemolysis index ≥ 0.85 across all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of agreement computed as 0.91 across five flow-rate/speed combinations from the FDA dataset. Systematic over-prediction of 8% at peak speed is within combined experimental and model uncertainty."
